<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thanks for your message</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600&family=Montserrat:wght@700&display=swap');
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eaf6fb 0%, #f4f7fa 100%);
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 540px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 36px 32px 28px 32px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(44, 204, 64, 0.10), 0 1.5px 8px rgba(44, 204, 64, 0.08);
            border-top: 8px solid #2ecc40;
        }
        .logo {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }
        .logo img {
            max-width: 160px;
            height: 80px;
            object-fit: contain;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 2px 8px rgba(44,204,64,0.10));
        }
        h3 {
            color: #1a2e35;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            text-align: center;
            letter-spacing: 1.2px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        p {
            color: #3a4a54;
            font-size: 17px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin: 14px 0;
            font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        strong {
            color: #2ecc40;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 36px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #7b8a8b;
            border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
            padding-top: 18px;
            text-align: center;
            font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 13px 32px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2ecc40 60%, #27ae60 100%);
            color: #fff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 17px;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', Arial, sans-serif;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(44,204,64,0.12);
            transition: background 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #27ae60 60%, #2ecc40 100%);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(44,204,64,0.18);
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                padding: 18px 8px 14px 8px;
            }
            h3 {
                font-size: 22px;
            }
            p {
                font-size: 15px;
            }
        }
        .faq-link {
            color: #2ecc40;
            text-decoration: underline;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="https://app-assets-bkt1.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/CR147-Logo.webp" 
                 alt="Croupier147 Logo" />
        </div>
        <h1>Thank You for Contacting Us!</h1>
        <p>Hi <%= @website_message.sender_name %>,</p>
        <p>
            The Croupier147 team has received your message.<br>
            We will be back in touch within the next <strong>24 to 48 hours</strong>.
        </p>
        <p>
            In the meantime, you can visit our 
            <a href="https://croupier147.com/faq" class="faq-link">FAQ page</a>
            for answers to common questions.
        </p>
        <div class="footer">
            Best Regards,<br>
            The Croupier147 Team
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>